description: I interviewed Bob Berg in Brooklyn, in 1998.  We did a Blindfold Test, he offered his ideas on some Desert Island discs, and he had a few things to say about Chick Corea (he was in Chick's band at the time). He also says something about his latest recording, at the time, Another Standard.
title: Bob Berg -  Unedited Interview  - 1998
